1
00:00:23,930 --> 00:00:26,310
[Adapted from a novel published on Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:26,330 --> 00:00:27,280
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:27,850 --> 00:00:29,310
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,340 --> 00:00:31,060
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:18,970
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:21,930
Thank you for your help.

7
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,840
You will be alive,

8
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,040
and no one will stop you.

9
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:27,920
But remember,

10
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:31,300
don't tell anyone about
the marriage contract.

11
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,440
Speaking of which,

12
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,680
I'm curious.

13
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,440
Why did Grand Pontiff

14
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,590
banish you

15
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:39,320
into that abyss?

16
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:46,310
[State Religious Academy]

17
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:56,960
No wonder Xu Shiji left
without saying anything.

18
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:58,520
This is why!

19
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,710
What was Grand Pontiff thinking?

20
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,100
This is not admission.

21
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,760
It's rather incarceration!

22
00:03:05,890 --> 00:03:08,280
[Religious]

23
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,440
Our country, the Great Zhou,
places great importance on religion.

24
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:13,440
State Religious Academy should be
the top one among  all the academies.

25
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,720
How could it be so shabby?

26
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,160
You are so knowledgeable,

27
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,720
and you didn't know about this?

28
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,200
There are no records of this

29
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:21,079
in the The Three Thousand
Daoist Scriptures I read.

30
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:21,840
Simply put,

31
00:03:22,730 --> 00:03:24,070
20 years ago,

32
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:25,550
[20 years ago, Shang Xingzhou,
the director of State Religious Academy,]

33
00:03:24,090 --> 00:03:26,150
Shang Xingzhou, the director
of State Religious Academy,

34
00:03:25,579 --> 00:03:26,460
[Tang Thirty-Six]

35
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:32,060
dissatisfied with the rule of
the Holy Empress of the Tianhai family,

36
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,170
led the whole academy to rebel.

37
00:03:34,170 --> 00:03:38,690
[Shang Xingzhou rebelled]
[Tang Thirty-Six]

38
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,880
State Religious Academy,

39
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:46,120
for the sake of the country,

40
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:48,240
respectfully request
that you abdicate immediately

41
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:50,770
and restore the legitimate rule
to the world.

42
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,840
That angered the almighty Grand Pontiff.

43
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,920
Shang.

44
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,400
You crossed the line.

45
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,520
In the end,

46
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,200
not only Shang Xingzhou,

47
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:17,310
but also all the staff and building
of State Religious Academy

48
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:17,700
[Seal]

49
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,320
have gone in a poof.

50
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,320
It sounds

51
00:04:24,450 --> 00:04:25,510
there's more to it.

52
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,740
No need to dig too deep!

53
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,080
What's important is

54
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,170
why Grand Pontiff

55
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:34,520
sends you to State Religious Academy
he destroyed himself?

56
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:40,370
He knew the Tianhai family
joined forces with five other acadamies

57
00:04:40,370 --> 00:04:42,880
to purge State Religious Academy.

58
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,130
Isn't this pushing you into a fire pit?

59
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,010
After all this talk,

60
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:53,680
do you still want to stay
in this ominous place?

61
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:59,090
Since I'm already here,
I might as well settle in.

62
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:02,650
This place looks a lot like the old temple
I used to stay when studying in Xining.

63
00:05:02,650 --> 00:05:03,170
Quiet.

64
00:05:03,490 --> 00:05:04,420
Close to nature.

65
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,120
I like this place.

66
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:10,320
Master said that only by participating
in the Imperial Court Exam

67
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:12,580
could I get a chance to change their fate.

68
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,920
It's my only choice to participate in it

69
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,960
as a student of State Religious Academy.

70
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:21,020
But you don't even have cultivation!

71
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,040
It's not that I can't cultivate.

72
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:25,100
I simply haven't cultivated before.

73
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:29,520
The candidates of the Imperial Court Exam
are all geniuses of the Continent.

74
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,320
Is it possible

75
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:34,040
that you're a natural-born cultivator,
able to break through realms in no time?

76
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,640
Let me check your meridians.

77
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,520
I've never seen this before.

78
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,800
Never!

79
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,520
I didn't expect…

80
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:47,280
that your meridians are so shattered!

81
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,800
The Imperial Court Exam
is only 3 months away.

82
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:51,600
Isn't it too late for you
to start cultivating now?

83
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:55,310
My master also said that my body
was different from that of others.

84
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,440
But he also once said

85
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:59,120
knowledge is acquired in its own time.

86
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,320
The latecomer may reach the goal first.

87
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,840
Three months from now,
at the Imperial Court Exam,

88
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:10,500
I shall seize the first place
on all the rosters.

89
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,060
[A Yard and A Star]

90
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:15,920
A yard and a star.

91
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:18,460
[The Young Director Episode 2]

92
00:06:21,580 --> 00:06:23,590
[Book Pavilion]

93
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,760
I can't believe that
in such a shabby place,

94
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:27,620
there is an intact book pavilion.

95
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:28,880
Good.

96
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,380
My cultivation

97
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,690
will start from opening this library.

98
00:06:33,130 --> 00:06:36,800
[Scripture Pavilion]

99
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,680
The mechanism lock
from the Central Directorate?

100
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,920
That's hard to open.

101
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,520
We need the key.

102
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,600
Key?

103
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:48,240
[Cleric Xin,
Senior Instructor of Central Directorate]

104
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,880
What key?

105
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,159
Which academy are you from?

106
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:52,620
State Religious Academy.

107
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,740
State Religious Academy?

108
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,720
Who is this brat?

109
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,000
How dare you fool me!

110
00:06:59,159 --> 00:06:59,680
Guards!

111
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:02,120
Drag him out and give him
20 strokes of the cane!

112
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:04,620
Teach him what respect is!

113
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:09,120
It's Grand Pontiff who
recommended me to the academy.

114
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,880
Grand Pontiff?

115
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,440
What are you waiting for?

116
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,640
Go loosen up his back!

117
00:07:16,850 --> 00:07:18,910
Sir, how's the pressure?

118
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,370
Tell me if it's not okay.

119
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,560
This is the recommendation letter.

120
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,620
Please have a look.

121
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:28,280
You are recommended by Grand Pontiff.

122
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:30,050
Of course I believe you.

123
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,480
Checking the recommendation letter

124
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,330
is just a standard process.

125
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,580
[The Grand Pontiff ordains:
Chen Changsheng, disciple of Xining is]

126
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,920
It's real!

127
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,390
[Admitted to State Religious Academy and
shall reside in Shendu; Guangming Hall]

128
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:41,270
As soon as you entered the room,
I noticed that you're quite elegant.

129
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:42,540
Tell me if you need anything.

130
00:07:42,540 --> 00:07:44,420
Leave everything to me!

131
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,320
I'm here to get the key to Book Pavilion.

132
00:07:48,470 --> 00:07:49,620
[Bank Note of the Great Zhou]

133
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,000
How can that be enough?

134
00:07:49,620 --> 00:07:50,350
[Student List]

135
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:50,640
Name list,

136
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,040
stamp,

137
00:07:51,050 --> 00:07:51,690
and bonus…

138
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,520
I've packed everything for you.

139
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,740
You even gave me the stamp of the academy?

140
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:00,120
You're the only one
in State Religious Academy.

141
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,200
According to the rules of the academy,

142
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:01,880
you

143
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,920
are the director.

144
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:35,960
These books are different from The Three
Thousand Daoist Scriptures I've read.

145
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,620
Besides, they're all intact.

146
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,320
How glorious State Religious Academy

147
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,850
must have been!

148
00:08:40,929 --> 00:08:41,919
We study

149
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,360
to cultivate our virtue.

150
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,880
Well said!

151
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:47,200
No loud talking in the pavilion!

152
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,460
Which class are you in?

153
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,280
It would be nice

154
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,460
if I could see those images again.

155
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,560
Director Chen!

156
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,660
You could have asked us

157
00:08:57,660 --> 00:09:01,200
-to do such physical labor.
-It's okay.

158
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,460
I quite like cleaning.

159
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,720
What a coincidence!

160
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,600
We love cleaning, too!

161
00:09:09,950 --> 00:09:12,410
You're appointed by Grand Pontiff himself.

162
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,000
You must be gifted.

163
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:16,280
Have you reached
the Realm of Seated Illumination?

164
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,110
No, I haven't.

165
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,840
If you've reached
the Realm of Marrow Cleansing,

166
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:28,370
you'll be considered a genius
who can enter the Blue Cloud List.

167
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,240
I haven't reached that, either.

168
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:32,890
That means you haven't
started your cultivation.

169
00:09:32,890 --> 00:09:36,180
[Marrow Cleansing Theory]

170
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,280
I'm about to…

171
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:35,480
start.

172
00:09:38,290 --> 00:09:40,660
[Plum Blossom Court]

173
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:41,200
He hasn't even started the cultivation
at the age of 16!

174
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,320
Master Meilisha.

175
00:09:42,550 --> 00:09:44,120
I really don't know

176
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:47,080
how to instruct this Director Chen!

177
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,760
No hurry.

178
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:53,530
[Meilisha, Cardinal
of the Central Directorate]

179
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:55,480
Don't panic.

180
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,560
Take your time.

181
00:10:02,620 --> 00:10:04,860
I'll be screwed if it goes on like this!

182
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:08,280
What is on Grand Pontiff's mind?

183
00:10:10,670 --> 00:10:13,470
Please show me the way!

184
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:17,230
Since you have swallowed it,

185
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:20,000
just digest it.

186
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,120
What?

187
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,920
Can I spit it out?

188
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:28,720
Good flowers do not fear late blooming.

189
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:32,920
Heaven bestows them with a fragrance.

190
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:35,200
Come stargazing with me.

191
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:39,400
There might be
something different tonight.

192
00:10:49,370 --> 00:10:51,330
[Marrow Cleansing Theory]

193
00:10:57,050 --> 00:11:01,000
March 19, vernal equinox,
the 1st day of my cultivation.

194
00:10:57,710 --> 00:11:01,050
[March 19, vernal equinox,
the 1st day of my cultivation]

195
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:17,160
Compared to the flower tea in Xining,

196
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,690
the tea in Shendu is not bad.

197
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:29,620
[Marrow Cleansing Theory]

198
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:31,560
The cultivation realms, arranged in
ascending order from lowest to highest,

199
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:32,840
are as follows: Marrow Cleansing,

200
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,840
Seated Illumination,

201
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,800
Approaching the Profound Truth,

202
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:35,730
Star Gathering,

203
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:36,680
Following the Sage,

204
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,080
and Divine Concealment.

205
00:11:38,850 --> 00:11:40,600
The first step of cultivation is

206
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,170
to light up the Destiny Star.

207
00:11:42,170 --> 00:11:44,040
You need to enter the Sea of Stars
with your Divine Consciousness

208
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:46,100
and find the star that belongs to you.

209
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,860
The stronger your Divine Consciousness is,

210
00:11:47,860 --> 00:11:50,480
the more potential
the Destiny Star you pick will be.

211
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,530
Reading can best develop
the Divine Consciousness.

212
00:11:52,530 --> 00:11:53,920
Master asked me to only read

213
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:55,000
and not to cultivate.

214
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,200
That's all for today.

215
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,780
I had ten years invested in

216
00:11:57,880 --> 00:12:00,080
The Three Thousand Daoist Scriptures.

217
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:01,700
Focus and condence

218
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,650
the Divine Consciousness!

219
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,100
So this is the Sea of Stars.

220
00:12:28,650 --> 00:12:30,250
Now, I see it with my own eyes.

221
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:33,720
It's more beautiful than
what the Scriptures described.

222
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,560
Next,

223
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,060
I need to find my Destiny Star.

224
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,010
It's over there!

225
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:57,370
I've never seen

226
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,100
such a majestic Destiny Star!

227
00:13:00,560 --> 00:13:02,000
It's above State Religious Academy!

228
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,860
Could it belong to Director Chen?

229
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:12,220
That star feels familiar.

230
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:13,840
Is it Junior?

231
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,840
His Destiny Star is powerful

232
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,400
but far away.

233
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,560
To succeed,

234
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:24,760
he must cross the Gate of Life and Death
in the Sea of Stars.

235
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:42,960
A wall?

236
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:45,680
There's actually a wall
in the Sea of Stars!

237
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:47,680
The Scriptures never mentioned it!

238
00:13:48,450 --> 00:13:49,320
However,

239
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:51,560
my star is guiding me forward.

240
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:00,080
A little touch

241
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:02,000
damages my Divine Consciousness greatly.

242
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,530
If I want to cross this wall,

243
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:06,960
I may die of the annihilation
of my Divine Consciousness.

244
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:07,920
But

245
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:10,720
this is just my first step
to change my fate.

246
00:14:24,680 --> 00:14:27,160
The more my
Divine Consciousness disappears,

247
00:14:27,160 --> 00:14:30,160
the weaker my perception
of the Destiny Star becomes.

248
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,950
Junior's aura

249
00:14:38,020 --> 00:14:38,960
has weakened.

250
00:14:41,020 --> 00:14:42,610
♪ The moist fog ♪

251
00:14:42,680 --> 00:14:44,660
♪ It's like walking in a dream ♪

252
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:46,390
♪ My eyes are sharp ♪

253
00:14:46,410 --> 00:14:48,240
♪ The hardest iron shovel on my back ♪

254
00:14:49,220 --> 00:14:50,750
♪ Going over that high mountain ♪

255
00:14:50,770 --> 00:14:52,040
♪ To take a look ♪

256
00:14:52,060 --> 00:14:53,780
♪ Holding the dinner in the cup ♪

257
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:55,630
♪ Going through swamps and mires ♪

258
00:14:55,660 --> 00:14:57,530
♪ All living beings are scattered ♪

259
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:58,000
Did I

260
00:14:57,570 --> 00:14:59,200
♪ No one accompanies me along the way ♪

261
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:00,200
make a wrong choice?

262
00:14:59,230 --> 00:15:01,110
♪ I don't feel lonely ♪

263
00:15:01,130 --> 00:15:03,770
♪ I don't worry about
being betrayed again ♪

264
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:04,480
Kid.

265
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:05,800
♪ The fog clears ♪

266
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:07,230
Once you step onto
the path of cultivation,

267
00:15:06,800 --> 00:15:08,440
♪ I encountered many obstacles ♪

268
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:08,830
you're destined to face
near-certain death.

269
00:15:08,470 --> 00:15:10,360
♪ It's not as difficult as I thought ♪

270
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,880
If you already know life is short,

271
00:15:10,380 --> 00:15:12,660
♪ It's just a lightning ♪

272
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:12,840
isn't it better

273
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:14,100
♪ It's just a setback ♪

274
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:14,130
to live a stable life?

275
00:15:14,130 --> 00:15:16,230
♪ I'm like an arrow loosed from the bow ♪

276
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:18,010
♪ I'd rather live the most tragic life ♪

277
00:15:18,030 --> 00:15:20,400
♪ I leave without saying goodbye ♪

278
00:15:20,420 --> 00:15:24,690
♪ Let's never meet again
if we have different paths ♪

279
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,520
The star is gone!

280
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:27,240
♪ It's just a lightning ♪

281
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:26,340
Director Chen has failed!

282
00:15:27,270 --> 00:15:28,810
♪ It's just a setback ♪

283
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,960
No hurry.

284
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:30,880
♪ I'm like an arrow loosed from the bow ♪

285
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,440
Just wait.

286
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:33,240
♪ I'd rather live the most tragic life ♪

287
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:34,680
This is not

288
00:15:35,280 --> 00:15:36,920
the way I want to live my life.

289
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,340
I want to live

290
00:15:39,390 --> 00:15:41,090
♪ All of a sudden ♪

291
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:43,160
because I don't want to be others' burden.

292
00:15:41,130 --> 00:15:43,180
♪ I want to go up
the mountain of swords ♪

293
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,560
♪ Looking down ♪

294
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,800
I want to live

295
00:15:44,590 --> 00:15:46,720
♪ Blood is my saddle ♪

296
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:49,000
to feel the beauty of this world.

297
00:15:46,740 --> 00:15:50,110
♪ I'm not afraid of the dark night ♪

298
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:50,960
I want to live

299
00:15:50,180 --> 00:15:52,360
♪ Let the red fill up the world ♪

300
00:15:52,380 --> 00:15:54,150
♪ It's a long journey and we'll see ♪

301
00:15:54,170 --> 00:15:55,770
♪ Scream ♪

302
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:57,340
♪ Sing my praises ♪

303
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:58,120
to fulfill

304
00:15:57,370 --> 00:15:59,410
♪ Climbing higher ♪

305
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,360
the promises to others!

306
00:15:59,430 --> 00:16:01,440
♪ I never felt cold ♪

307
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,040
Little Taoist Monk.

308
00:16:01,460 --> 00:16:04,170
♪ My entire body is able to relax ♪

309
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:04,200
When you grow up, come find me in Shendu.

310
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:06,880
♪ Let the world turn upside down ♪

311
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:06,910
There is so much delicious food
and so many fun things to do here.

312
00:16:06,910 --> 00:16:08,720
♪ No matter whether the future is bright or dark ♪

313
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,640
I'll take you to eat braised beef bone

314
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:09,960
and visit the Heavenly Book Mausoleum

315
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,080
and the Bridge of Helplessness.

316
00:16:10,950 --> 00:16:11,730
[Little Taoist Monk, if you
come to Shendu, do come find me.]

317
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:13,300
[There is plenty of delicious food here;
I'll take you to eat braised beef bone.]

318
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:19,560
My star…

319
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,440
is helping me.

320
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:29,470
I want my life

321
00:16:30,650 --> 00:16:32,040
to go the way I want!

322
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:44,600
Yes!

323
00:16:44,830 --> 00:16:46,840
Just lit up the Destiny Star, and he's
already made such a splendid display!

324
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:49,720
Director Chen indeed
has infinite potential!

325
00:16:51,160 --> 00:16:52,640
Didn't the flower

326
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:55,760
just bloom?

327
00:17:00,660 --> 00:17:03,010
What an amazing star!

328
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:07,520
On the day of vernal equinox,
Little Taoist Monk

329
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:08,960
stepped onto the path of cultivation.

330
00:17:07,650 --> 00:17:09,280
♪ All of a sudden ♪

331
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:11,240
♪ I want to go up
the mountain of swords ♪

332
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,430
The Destiny Star he lit

333
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:13,030
♪ Looking down ♪

334
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:12,800
makes the whole city of Shendu

335
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:14,520
shine together.

336
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:15,030
♪ Blood is my saddle ♪

337
00:17:15,270 --> 00:17:18,640
♪ I'm not afraid of the dark night ♪

338
00:17:18,119 --> 00:17:19,680
What an amazing Destiny Star!

339
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:20,500
♪ Let the red fill up the world ♪

340
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:22,300
♪ It's a long journey and we'll see ♪

341
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:23,960
♪ Scream ♪

342
00:17:24,109 --> 00:17:26,160
♪ Sing my praises ♪

343
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:27,700
♪ Climbing higher ♪

344
00:17:27,839 --> 00:17:29,680
♪ Fill up the wine cup ♪

345
00:17:29,870 --> 00:17:33,330
♪ I drink with the Moon ♪

346
00:17:33,870 --> 00:17:35,040
♪ Without realizing it,
I'm already ashore ♪

347
00:17:35,330 --> 00:17:37,170
♪ There's no need
to sigh about success or failure ♪

348
00:17:48,630 --> 00:17:56,360
[Marrow Cleansing — star-tempered body,
immune to illness, and able to lift rocks]

349
00:18:05,800 --> 00:18:07,040
It smells so good.

350
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:12,160
Miss.

351
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:16,120
Since the Destiny Star is so powerful,

352
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:17,440
his Divine Consciousness must be so, too.

353
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,440
Maybe…

354
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:19,840
he can cure me.

355
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:21,000
Miss,

356
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:22,160
please come down.

357
00:18:22,320 --> 00:18:23,160
It's dangerous up there.

358
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:24,120
Don't fall down.

359
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,610
If I bring these guys over,

360
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:32,460
they'll terrify him for sure.

361
00:18:33,560 --> 00:18:35,540
[Thousand-Mile Talisman —
instant travel across a thousand miles]

362
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,280
Oh no!

363
00:18:39,280 --> 00:18:41,600
Her… Miss is missing!

364
00:18:45,080 --> 00:18:46,200
I'll go find her.

365
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:47,920
Hurry up and report it.

366
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:48,640
Yes!

367
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:55,840
You didn't expect that
I'm just coming to next door, did you?

368
00:18:55,840 --> 00:18:58,370
Uncle Jin won't locate me
so easily this time.

369
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:05,400
It's him!

370
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:18,000
Your Highness.

371
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:21,170
I've been waiting for you
for such a long time.

372
00:19:31,460 --> 00:19:33,020
Don't you all want more?

373
00:19:33,090 --> 00:19:35,090
I asked the white crane
to bring you a surprise.

374
00:19:35,090 --> 00:19:36,890
Please scan the QR code to watch.

375
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:42,990
[In the next episode]

376
00:19:39,390 --> 00:19:40,640
You want to become my disciple?

377
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:41,150
Why?

378
00:19:42,100 --> 00:19:43,830
My meridians are problematic.

379
00:19:44,220 --> 00:19:47,390
No one has ever forced me to
resort to Zhongshan Storm Sword.

380
00:19:47,390 --> 00:19:48,600
You are the only one.

381
00:19:49,220 --> 00:19:50,600
I'm not eligible to teach you.

382
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:52,260
Nor do I have time to teach you.

383
00:19:52,990 --> 00:19:53,980
Guozi.

384
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:55,920
Where are you?

385
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:57,980
We're not the same kind of people.

386
00:19:58,260 --> 00:19:58,900
Go back.

387
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:00,150
Don't come back again.

